newsitem.title: UK: SOCCER-SCOTTISH F.A. CUP FIRST AND SECOND ROUND DRAW.
newsitem.headline: SOCCER-SCOTTISH F.A. CUP FIRST AND SECOND ROUND DRAW.

text.p: The draw for the first and second rounds of the
Scottish F.A. Cup made on Wednesday:
First round (Saturday, Dec 7): Elgin v Whitehill Welfare, Albion Rovers v
Forfar, Alloa v Hawick, Huntly v Clyde.
Second round (Saturday, Jan 4): Stranrear v Inverness Caledonian Thistle,
Ross County v Montrose, Spartans v Arbroath, Berwick v Peterhead, Queens Park v
Gala, Elgin or Whitehill v Queen of the South, Brechin v Livingstone, East
Stirling v Brora, Stenhousemuir v Hamilton, Ayr v Huntley or Clyde, Cowdenbeath
v Dumbarton, Albion Rovers or Forfar v Alloa or Hawick.
